202
00:15:41.231 --> 00:15:42.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Accomplish?

203
00:15:42.942 --> 00:15:44.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
