206
00:15:47.905 --> 00:15:50.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

207
00:15:50.699 --> 00:15:52.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
