218
00:16:16.141 --> 00:16:17.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kill them?

219
00:16:19.687 --> 00:16:23.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
