222
00:16:36.829 --> 00:16:38.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Saying this distresses him.</i>

223
00:16:39.289 --> 00:16:42.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>This is what humans are.</i>

224
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:47.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
