the means of distinguishing

233
00:17:13.532 --> 00:17:15.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
between human beings and parasites.

234
00:17:15.951 --> 00:17:17.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
