235
00:17:17.953 --> 00:17:20.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Wait. We have a way to do that?

236
00:17:20.372 --> 00:17:21.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
To tell them apart?

237
00:17:21.457 --> 00:17:25.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll let Dr. Yui explain.

238
00:17:27.880 --> 00:17:30.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'll now explain
what we've uncovered so far

239
00:17:30.758 --> 00:17:33.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
regarding the parasite's physiology.

240
00:17:34.970 --> 00:17:37.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This parasitic life form has the ability
to serve as the human brain,

241
00:17:37.973 --> 00:17:40.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that is, the command center
of the entire body,

242
00:17:40.893 --> 00:17:44.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and to push it beyond
its physiological limits.

243
00:17:44.146 --> 00:17:47.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
