244
00:17:47.483 --> 00:17:51.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
but could be characterized
as sentient muscle.

245
00:17:51.612 --> 00:17:54.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Sentient muscle".

246
00:17:54.948 --> 00:17:56.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
