247
00:17:56.867 --> 00:17:58.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
They can morph in an instant

248
00:17:58.827 --> 00:18:02.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
to stretch like rubber
or become as hard as steel.

249
00:18:02.331 --> 00:18:06.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Then, how can such an alien cell type
form connections with the human body?

250
00:18:07.544 --> 00:18:10.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
