253
00:18:16.011 --> 00:18:17.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
please tell us how
to tell them apart first.

254
00:18:17.387 --> 00:18:18.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

255
00:18:20.724 --> 00:18:21.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So…

256
00:18:22.768 --> 00:18:26.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
