what do you think happens?

259
00:18:35.989 --> 00:18:38.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If they cannot secure blood circulation,
they shrivel up and die,

260
00:18:39.076 --> 00:18:41.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
