with other cells of their kind.

261
00:18:41.411 --> 00:18:44.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Should they become a fragment
about the size of a hair,

262
00:18:44.581 --> 00:18:46.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
