269
00:19:02.307 --> 00:19:03.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
In other words,

270
00:19:04.476 --> 00:19:08.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
